{"tid":2507973,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"失業貸款即日起接受申請 有冇清狗衝咗？","createTime":"2021-04-28T11:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T07:24:12.000Z","uid":218407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0bb48301caefe27cef87efe118c8ef649e5c4c7a","tid":2507973,"uid":218407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:29:45.000Z","msg":"政府早前提出的「百分百擔保個人特惠貸款計劃」，今日（28日）起接受申請。按證保險公司宣布俗稱「失業貸款」的計劃詳情，凡18歲或以上香港永久性居民，失業至少2個月的合資格申請人，即可於4月28日至10月27日進行申請，貸款上限8萬元、實除年利率1厘。合資格申請人需為18歲或以上的香港永久性居民，申請失業至少2個月，並須證明已失去在港就業所得的主要經常收入。同時，申請人須提交2020年1月至2021年2月期間，至少3個月的工作和主要經常收入證明。<br />\n<br />\n申請期咁耐 有冇人知幾時先收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be87f2f628ed721673068c29ade41509ea02b2e","tid":2507973,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:31:25.000Z","msg":"攞去做td都有賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fcca852bd023568b5fdcfc3fc54d56d3a0d13dd","tid":2507973,"uid":219362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7be87f2f628ed721673068c29ade41509ea02b2e","tid":2507973,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:31:25.000Z","msg":"攞去做td都有賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:31:52.000Z","msg":"td即係咩?"},{"pid":"58355475dc49313ca7854294b4beb464d9eed74c","tid":2507973,"uid":118074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:31:59.000Z","msg":"要失業兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9c296b5ae5ff4b6dc5a30b3494c96991a17562","tid":2507973,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9fcca852bd023568b5fdcfc3fc54d56d3a0d13dd","tid":2507973,"uid":219362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7be87f2f628ed721673068c29ade41509ea02b2e","tid":2507973,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1